{"tid":1906191,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"包裹播毒？美國郵政署員工中咗武漢肺炎！","createTime":"2020-03-01T18:27:45.000Z","updateTime":"2020-03-02T04:30:08.000Z","uid":28114,"like":9,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":25,"replies":[{"pid":"c5bb8b4cd239a92ad3b934a4b51d32e18a41933e","tid":1906191,"uid":28114,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-01T18:27:45.000Z","msg":"Local USPS employee tests positive for coronavirus<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://cmg-cmg-tv-10090-prod.cdn.arcpublishing.com/ampiframe/?id=4850552#amp=1\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcmg-cmg-tv-10090-prod.cdn.arcpublishing.com%2Fampiframe%2F%3Fid%3D4850552%23amp%3D1&d=cG87S%2FC0TFnLRhO0hL0igfilxGv0e2UEk%2F7kpEYl8nk%3D&h=3dccc86a\" target=\"_blank\">https://cmg-cmg-tv-10090-prod.cdn.arcpublishing.com/ampiframe/?id=4850552#amp=1</a><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.kiro7.com/news/local/local-usps-employee-tests-positive-coronavirus/XLKCBEXO5FFJ3DRQSBHNACPW2M/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.kiro7.com%2Fnews%2Flocal%2Flocal-usps-employee-tests-positive-coronavirus%2FXLKCBEXO5FFJ3DRQSBHNACPW2M%2F&d=cG87S%2FC0TFnLRhO0hL0igfilxGv0e2UEk%2F7kpEYl8nk%3D&h=d821f35f\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.kiro7.com/news/local/local-usps-employee-tests-positive-coronavirus/XLKCBEXO5FFJ3DRQSBHNACPW2M/</a><br />\n<br />\nUpdated: February 29, 2020 - 10:47 PM<br />\nFEDERAL WAY, Wash. &mdash; KIRO 7 found out Saturday evening that a Seattle area U.S. Postal Service employee tested positive for the coronavirus.<br />\nA corporate communications spokesperson said that the employee works at a Seattle Network Distribution Center located in Federal Way.<br />\nThe Network Distribution Center is a mail processing plant that distributes USPS marketing mail and package services in piece and bulk form and does not handle letter mail. No mail is delivered from the facility.<br />\n<br />\nThe spokesperson said USPS has been consulting with the county health department and was informed that the risk to other employees is low.<br />\nKIRO 7 was also told that USPS will continue to follow the recommended strategies from the county and federal health officials.<br />\nBelow is a statement from a USPS corporate communications field representative from Washington.<br />\n&ldquo;The Network Distribution Center does not handle letter mail - only parcels. No mail is delivered from the facility. It is sorted and transported to individual post offices, from which the parcels are delivered to customers. The employee in question works within the facility. The employee would have some contact with other employees in the work environment.&rdquo;"},{"pid":"35fc1393ff1329ec5efdab1e9ef1bbc20ad0bbaf","tid":1906191,"uid":232250,"like":11,"dislike":0,"score":11,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-03-01T18:36:24.000Z","msg":"之前話病毒可以係非活體生存到九日，唔知係咪真。"},{"pid":"6224dc0774a452eec2942b7a94443e3d4dc36dbb","tid":1906191,"uid":4519,"like":11,"dislike":0,"score":11,"quote":{"pid":"35fc1393ff1329ec5efdab1e9ef1bbc20ad0bbaf","tid":1906191,"uid":232250,"like":11,"dislike":0,"score":11,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-03-01T18:36:24.000Z","msg":"之前話病毒可以係非活體生存到九日，唔知係咪真。"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-01T18:39:56.000Z","msg":"唔怪得bns咁撚慢啦，真係用心良苦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a5f4bc96ca54ab4e59b67dfbbc782668e2a12987","tid":1906191,"uid":127905,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-01T18:48:50.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>was informed that the risk to other employees is low</strong></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\nRAP"},{"pid":"a77ddd25ed63ac5abf10894f645eea782cb90558","tid":1906191,"uid":24345,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-01T19:12:03.000Z","msg":"美國其實拎夠證據宣布中國輸出病毒未"},{"pid":"9b67b458a338674d79abcc82485749dfcaba1425","tid":1906191,"uid":266289,"like":0,